# The Bitcoin Harmonic Time Model
### Internal Phase Symmetry, Amplitude Power-Laws, and the Institutional ETF Regime Shift

Author: **Romero Quant** Twitter/X: [@RomeroQuant](https://x.com/RomeroQuant)  
Date: June 2026  

