## Abstract
This repository contains the official whitepaper and core framework for the **Bitcoin Harmonic Time Model**. Moving away from traditional halving-centric models, this research formalises Bitcoin's price discovery as a continuous, two-dimensional dynamic system governed by an invariant temporal phase ratio ($\sim 1,060$ days of expansion followed by $\sim 370$ days of contraction) and a non-linear power-law amplitude decay ($\hat{\mathcal{M}}(d) = 328 \cdot d^{5.1}$).

